In order to install this module, first run

perl Makefile.PL

If this command says that some prerequisite modules are not present,
you need to install these modules; each required one should
be shipped with this package, and found in the "modules" directory.
If not, fetch them from CPAN at http://www.cpan.org/

make
make test
make install

This module depends on:

	Perl 5.005
	Class::MethodMaker 0.96	available from CPAN; http://www.cpan.org/
	GnuPG			available from http://www.gnupg.org/


